REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_B1A_1_VIDEO1
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1Karma: ^7Colonel Kurtz..."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_B1A_1_VIDEO2
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1Karma: ^7Celerium WORM, attacking the electrical grid. Power stations...water distribution...it's every state...oh wait...it's all over the world."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_B1A_1_VIDEO3
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1Col. Kurtz: ^7Get me the President!"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_B1A_1_VIDEO4
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1Karma: ^7Chill out jerkoff, I got it."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_B1A_2_VIDEO3
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1President Bosworth: ^7On behalf of our great nation, thank you."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_B2D_1_VIDEO1
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1CIA Nerd: ^7It's a Celerium WORM, mate. Same twat that copped the drones."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_B2D_1_VIDEO2
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1CIA Nerd: ^7It's knackered power stations all over the east coast."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_B2D_1_VIDEO3
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1Col. Kurtz: ^7How long will it take you to stop it?"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_B2D_1_VIDEO4
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1CIA Nerd: ^7I've spent the last year trying to crack this sod. Best thing I can do right now is leggit back to England."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_B3R_1_VIDEO1
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1Menendez: ^7This video is triggered to play upon my assassination. Cordis Die, you know how to proceed. My death will shine light upon ubiquitous darkness..."

