LANG_ENGLISH        "^1Soldier: ^7The Obama is secured!"

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_COM_2_VIDEO3
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1Soldier: ^7All hands, abandon ship! The Obama is lost."

REFERENCE           VIDSUBTITLES_COMA_1_VIDEO1
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1Briggs: ^7I have a thousand drones at standby alert, ready to launch on my command. If Russia or SDC gets any bright ideas, make no mistake Secretary Petraeus, your armed forces are ready."

